<view class='padding-30'>
<view class='h3 txt-black txt-blod margin-top margin-left-40 margin-right-40'>请选择您的身份</view>
<view class='h4-5  margin-left-40 margin-right-40 margin-top-20'>为了更好的使用本平台，请正确选择</view>
<view class='h4-5  margin-left-40 margin-right-40 margin-top-20'>您的身份</view>
</view>

<view class='flex-row flex-column margin-top-60'>

<navigator bindtap='bindtodriver'  class='margin-top flex-row flex-center driver_bg' >
